---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CtaSection from '../components/CtaSection.astro';
import TestimonialsCarousel from '../components/TestimonialsCarousel.astro';

const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Service",
  "name": "Risk Planning",
  "description": "We help you prepare for the unexpected with a risk strategy that protects your income, your family, and your future.",
  "provider": {
    "@type": "FinancialService",
    "name": "Simple Wealth",
    "url": "https://simplewealth.co.za"
  },
  "areaServed": { "@type": "Country", "name": "South Africa" },
  "serviceType": "Risk Planning"
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Risk Planning — Simple Wealth"
  description="We help you prepare for the unexpected with a risk strategy that protects your income, your family, and your future."
  activePage="risk-planning"
  showSocialInFooter={false}
  schema={schema}
>
  <section class="hero hero--short">
    <div class="hero__inner">
      <span class="service-hero-badge fade-up">Risk Planning</span>
      <h1 class="fade-up">Protect what you've worked so hard to build</h1>
      <p class="fade-up">Life doesn't always go to plan. We help you prepare for the unexpected with a risk strategy that protects your income, your family, and your future &mdash; so you're financially secure no matter what life throws at you.</p>
      <div class="btn-group fade-up">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--primary">Book a free call</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header fade-up">
        <h2>Do any of these risk concerns sound familiar?</h2>
        <p>Planning for risk can feel like a guessing game &mdash; especially when policies are complex, expensive, or hard to compare. Whether you're worried about losing your income, protecting your loved ones, or just unsure what cover you actually need, we help bring clarity and confidence to the what-ifs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cards-grid">
        <div class="card problem-card fade-up">
          <div class="card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Your family would struggle without your income</h3>
          <p>If something happened to you, would your loved ones be financially secure? Many people haven't planned for this scenario.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card problem-card fade-up">
          <div class="card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="20" height="14" x="2" y="5" rx="2"/><line x1="2" x2="22" y1="10" y2="10"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>You have no backup if business income stops</h3>
          <p>As a business owner, your income is directly tied to your ability to work. A gap in earnings could have serious consequences.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card problem-card fade-up">
          <div class="card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>You're worried about critical illness or disability</h3>
          <p>A serious illness can change everything overnight. Proper protection ensures you can focus on recovery, not finances.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card problem-card fade-up">
          <div class="card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/><path d="M12 17h.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>You're unsure what insurance you really need</h3>
          <p>With so many types of cover available, it's hard to know which policies are essential and which are unnecessary.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--grey">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header fade-up">
        <h2>Our approach to risk planning</h2>
        <p>We help you understand your real risks, protect what matters most, and create a safety net that gives you peace of mind. With the right protection in place, you can focus on living &mdash; not worrying. We make sure your risks are understood, managed and fully covered.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cards-grid">
        <div class="card fade-up">
          <div class="card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Protection for life's unexpected moments</h3>
          <p>We help you identify the biggest financial risks in your life &mdash; like illness, loss of income, or death &mdash; and put practical safeguards in place.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-up">
          <div class="card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Cover that works when you need it</h3>
          <p>We recommend only policies with strong claims records and help you understand what's covered &mdash; and what's not &mdash; before you commit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-up">
          <div class="card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>No blind spots, no guesswork</h3>
          <p>We review what you already have (or think you have) and spot the gaps &mdash; so you're not caught out when it matters most.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-up">
          <div class="card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8"/><path d="M21 3v5h-5"/><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16"/><path d="M3 21v-5h5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Adapts as your life changes</h3>
          <p>As your responsibilities grow &mdash; a family, a home, a business &mdash; we make sure your protection keeps pace without overcomplicating things.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <TestimonialsCarousel grey={false} />

  <section class="section section--grey">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header fade-up">
        <h2>Questions you may have on our risk service</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list fade-up">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">How do you decide what protection I need?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg></button>
          <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer__inner"><p>We conduct a thorough review of your financial situation, dependants, lifestyle, and obligations. This helps us identify where you're most vulnerable and recommend only the cover that genuinely makes sense for your circumstances.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">Will you review my existing insurance policies?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg></button>
          <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer__inner"><p>Absolutely. Many clients come to us with policies they've never reviewed. We'll assess what you already have, check for gaps or overlaps, and make sure your cover is still fit for purpose.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">Are your recommendations fully independent and unbiased?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg></button>
          <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer__inner"><p>Yes. We're not tied to any product providers, so our recommendations are based solely on what's best for you. We search the whole market to find the right protection at the right price.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">Do you handle the application and paperwork?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg></button>
          <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer__inner"><p>Yes, we handle the entire process from start to finish. From sourcing quotes to completing applications and liaising with insurers, we take care of everything so you don't have to.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">How do you balance affordability with good protection?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg></button>
          <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer__inner"><p>We work within your budget to prioritise the most critical risks first. It's not about having every policy available &mdash; it's about having the right ones in place that provide meaningful protection where it counts.</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaSection />
</BaseLayout>
